## 4. Asset Management

### Directory Structure

```
cognalith-website/public/
├── favicon.svg          # SVG favicon
├── og-image.png         # Open Graph image (1200x630)
├── og-image.svg         # Source SVG
├── robots.txt           # SEO
├── sitemap.xml          # SEO
└── images/              # Static images
```

### Asset Usage

```tsx
// Static imports (recommended for Next.js optimization)
import Image from "next/image";

<Image
  src="/images/hero.png"
  alt="Description"
  width={800}
  height={600}
  priority // For above-fold images
/>

// Or direct paths
<img src="/favicon.svg" alt="Logo" />
```

### Image Optimization

- Use `next/image` for automatic optimization
- SVG for icons and logos
- WebP/PNG for photos with `priority` prop for LCP images
- OG images: 1200x630px PNG

