## 5. Icon System

### Library

**Lucide React** - https://lucide.dev

### Import Pattern

```tsx
import {
  ArrowRight,
  Sparkles,
  Brain,
  Code,
  Shield
} from "lucide-react";
```

### Usage Pattern

```tsx
// Inline with text
<span className="flex items-center gap-2">
  <Sparkles className="w-4 h-4 text-accent-cyan" />
  Label
</span>

// In buttons
<Button>
  Next <ArrowRight className="ml-2 w-5 h-5" />
</Button>

// Colored icons
<Brain className="w-6 h-6" style={{ color: "#00d4ff" }} />
```

### Size Convention

| Usage | Class | Size |
|-------|-------|------|
| Inline text | `w-4 h-4` | 16px |
| Buttons | `w-5 h-5` | 20px |
| Cards | `w-6 h-6` | 24px |
| Features | `w-7 h-7` | 28px |
| Hero | `w-8 h-8` | 32px |

### Icon Naming

Use semantic names from Lucide. Common mappings:
- AI/Brain → `Brain`
- Code/Dev → `Code`
- Security → `Shield`
- Arrow → `ArrowRight`, `ChevronRight`
- Stars/Special → `Sparkles`, `Star`

