## 6. Styling Approach

### Methodology

**Tailwind CSS** with utility-first approach + custom CSS classes in `globals.css`.

### CSS Layers

```css
/* app/globals.css */

@layer base {
  /* Reset and base styles */
  body {
    @apply bg-dark text-text-primary font-sans antialiased;
  }
}

@layer components {
  /* Reusable component classes */
  .gradient-text {
    @apply bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-cyan via-accent-purple to-accent-cyan
           bg-clip-text text-transparent;
    background-size: 200% auto;
    animation: gradient 3s linear infinite;
  }

  .glow-border { /* ... */ }
  .card-hover { /* ... */ }
}

@layer utilities {
  /* Custom utilities */
  .perspective-1000 { perspective: 1000px; }
  .preserve-3d { transform-style: preserve-3d; }
}
```

### Custom Component Classes

| Class | Usage |
|-------|-------|
| `.gradient-text` | Animated gradient text |
| `.glow-border` | Glowing border effect |
| `.card-hover` | Hover lift animation |
| `.perspective-1000` | 3D perspective container |
| `.preserve-3d` | 3D child preservation |

### Responsive Breakpoints

Tailwind defaults:
- `sm:` → 640px
- `md:` → 768px
- `lg:` → 1024px
- `xl:` → 1280px
- `2xl:` → 1536px

**Usage Pattern:**
```tsx
<h1 className="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-7xl">
  Responsive Headline
</h1>
```

### Animation Classes

```typescript
// tailwind.config.ts
animation: {
  "fade-in": "fadeIn 0.5s ease-out",
  "slide-up": "slideUp 0.5s ease-out",
  "pulse-slow": "pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite",
  "glow": "glow 2s ease-in-out infinite",
}
```

