## 8. Figma MCP Integration Guidelines

### When Importing from Figma

1. **Extract Colors**: Map Figma color styles to `accent-*`, `dark-*`, `text-*` tokens
2. **Extract Typography**: Use closest Tailwind text size, not custom values
3. **Extract Spacing**: Round to 4px grid (Tailwind's spacing scale)
4. **Extract Components**: Create in `components/ui/` if reusable

### Component Mapping Rules

| Figma Component | React Component |
|-----------------|-----------------|
| Button/Primary | `<Button variant="primary">` |
| Button/Secondary | `<Button variant="secondary">` |
| Button/Ghost | `<Button variant="outline">` |
| Card | `<Card>` |
| Container | `<Container>` |
| Icon/* | `<IconName />` from lucide-react |

### Animation Guidelines

Use Framer Motion for all animations:

```tsx
import { motion } from "framer-motion";

// Entrance animation
<motion.div
  initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }}
  whileInView={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
  viewport={{ once: true }}
  transition={{ duration: 0.5 }}
>

// Hover animation
<motion.div
  whileHover={{ scale: 1.02, y: -5 }}
  whileTap={{ scale: 0.98 }}
>
```

### Section Template

```tsx
"use client";

import { motion } from "framer-motion";
import Container from "@/components/ui/Container";

export default function SectionName() {
  return (
    <section id="section-id" className="py-32 relative">
      {/* Background */}
      <div className="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-dark via-dark-secondary to-dark" />

      <Container className="relative z-10">
        {/* Header */}
        <motion.div
          initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }}
          whileInView={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
          viewport={{ once: true }}
          className="text-center mb-16"
        >
          <span className="text-accent-cyan text-sm tracking-wider uppercase">
            Section Label
          </span>
          <h2 className="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mt-4">
            Section <span className="gradient-text">Title</span>
          </h2>
        </motion.div>

        {/* Content */}
        <div className="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          {/* Items */}
        </div>
      </Container>
    </section>
  );
}
```

